window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>She planned her own funeral. But did she arrange her murder?</b> </p> <p>Buried secrets, murder and a trail of bloody clues lie at the heart of Anthony Horowitz's new detective series. If you enjoyed BBC's <i>Sherlock</i>, you'll love <i>The Word is Murder!</i> </p> <p>A wealthy woman strangled six hours after she's arranged her own funeral. </p> <p>A very private detective uncovering secrets but hiding his own. </p> <p>A reluctant author drawn into a story he can't control. </p> <p>What do they have in common? </p>"; 
